&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Sri-Ramakrishna.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">गुर्वष्टकम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%9F%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
